‘What underlines that? “Screw the country. We're going to do whatever we can to get this black man out of here”.’

Mr Morgan is concerned by the rise of the Tea Party, a right-wing Republican arm that supports presidential candidate Michele Bachmann.

‘It just shows the weak, dark, underside of America,’ he told CNN. ‘We're supposed to be better than that. We really are.

